## 8. Risk Assessment

### 8.1 Technical Risks

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Neon cold start latency | Medium | Low | Connection pooling, keep-alive |
| S3 CORS misconfiguration | Medium | Medium | Test thoroughly before launch |
| CloudFront cache invalidation delays | Low | Low | Use versioned URLs for updates |
| GitHub Actions timeout | Low | Medium | 10-minute timeout, optimize steps |
| Vercel free tier bandwidth limits | Medium | Medium | Monitor usage, plan upgrade path |

### 8.2 Operational Risks

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| AWS credentials leak | Low | Critical | Vercel env vars only, IAM least privilege |
| Neon branch confusion | Low | Medium | Clear naming convention, documentation |
| Accidental prod deployment | Low | High | Branch protection, manual QA → Prod |
| Cost overruns | Medium | Medium | Set billing alerts, monitor usage |

### 8.3 Mitigation Actions

1. **Credentials:** Store all secrets in Vercel dashboard, never in code
2. **Branch Protection:** Enable branch protection on `main` and `qa`
3. **Monitoring:** Set up billing alerts on AWS and Neon
4. **Documentation:** Document all infrastructure components and access

---

## 9. Cost Considerations

### 9.1 Free Tier Limits

| Service | Free Tier | Usage Estimate | Risk |
|---------|-----------|----------------|------|
| **Neon** | 3 GB storage, 1 project | <500 MB initially | Low |
| **Vercel** | 100 GB bandwidth | <10 GB initially | Low |
| **GitHub Actions** | 2000 min/month (private) | ~500-1000 min | Low |
| **AWS S3** | 5 GB storage, 20K GET | <1 GB initially | Low |
| **CloudFront** | 1 TB/month | <10 GB initially | Low |

### 9.2 Cost Optimization Implemented

| Optimization | Saving |
|--------------|--------|
| Neon auto-suspend (dev/qa) | Compute costs when idle |
| CloudFront PriceClass_100 | ~40% vs global |
| S3 no versioning (initially) | Storage costs |
| GitHub Actions caching | ~50% time savings |

